svg.text: IN EVERY ONE OF US THERE LIES A SEED OF GEEKINESS.
MARVEL AT THE VASTNESS OF WHAT CAN BE LEARNT.
BE HUMBLE. BE RECEPTIVE TO ALL FEEDBACK.
CONNECT IDEAS FROM VASTLY DIFFERENT DOMAINS. EXPERIMENT.
TAKE EVERY LITTLE STEP, EVERY LITTLE DETAIL, EVERY LITTLE DESIRE,
EVERY LITTLE DISCOMFORT, EVERY LITTLE JOY INTO THE JOURNEY
THAT MAKES US WHO WE TRULY ARE.
IT IS IN THE DOING THAT WE VASTLY IMPROVE OUR CRAFT.
